## Ledger — текущая реализация

### Domain

```
Ledger.Domain/
└── Entities/
    └── BankTransaction.cs      # ExternalId, Date, Amount, Currency, Description, Category?
```

### Application

```
Ledger.Application/
├── Banking/
│   ├── IBankDataProvider.cs    # application service interface
│   ├── BankDataProvider.cs     # оркестрация параллельной пагинации
│   ├── BankDataProviderOptions.cs   # PageSize, MaxParallelRequests
│   └── BankTransactionQuery.cs      # From, To, Offset, PageSize
└── Ports/
    └── IBankClient.cs          # outbound port — один запрос к банку
```

### Infrastructure

```
Ledger.Infrastructure/
└── Banking/Banks/
    └── Mock/
        └── MockBankClient.cs   # тестовый адаптер IBankClient
```

### Api

```
Ledger.Api/
├── Program.cs                  # composition root
└── Extensions/
    └── BankingExtensions.cs    # AddLedgerApplication(...)
```

### Tests

```
Ledger.Tests/
└── Banking/
    └── BankDataProviderTests.cs
```

